Call Action - move arm:
ros2 action send_goal /joint_ptp_action wx250s_interface/action/JointPTP "{joint_goal: [0, 28, -56, -1, -56, 4]}"

Call Service - home arm (/homing):
ros2 service call /homing std_srvs/srv/Trigger

Publish to Topic - gripper state (bool):
ros2 topic pub /grip std_msgs/msg/Bool '{data: False}'



Build + Install:
colcon build
source install/setup.bash

Launch Package:
ros2 launch wx250s joint_ptp_launch.xml
